---
By: Dalai Lama
Source:
  URL: https://twitter.com/DalaiLama/status/988103930113679360
  Locus:
    Date: 22 April 2018
---
Humanity's thirst for natural resources can only be sustained if we adapt
our patterns of consumption. Competition for necessities like water, food
and land will inevitably intensify. To meet the challenge of climate change
and environmental depletion we must all cooperate.
